And his company’s history of chopping down local newspapers for profit is a real threat to the First Amendment and the society it is intended to protect.
Selling us less news and information packaged as “quality local journalism” is a means to that end.
The decline of local newspapers is a real threat to democracy.
The Santa Fe New Mexican remains one of the strongest local newspapers around.
